sequenceDiagram
    participant Att as Attacker
    participant BE as Backend
    participant GW as Gateway

    rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
    Note over Att,BE: Before mitigation
    Att->>BE: Direct call + X-Role: admin
    BE-->>Att: 200 allowed
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
    Note over Att,GW: After mitigation
    Att->>BE: Direct call + forged headers
    BE-->>Att: 403 untrusted caller
    Att->>GW: Request via gateway
    GW->>BE: Signed headers + trusted identity
    BE-->>GW: 200 allowed (policy-compliant)
    end
